data.description: This is just not any home, its THE HOME!  Country setting surrounded by fields & backed by woods, this traditional brick home offers 3Br 2.5Ba, open living room with fireplace, kitchen, breakfast area and formal dining room, foyer, office and large laundry room.  Perfect for summer to enjoy the in ground approximately 18x30 pool.   Pool house encloses well pump & pool filter equipment. Attached 2 car garage as well as detached completely finished 2 car garage/shop with A/C.  Enclosed screen porch by pool.  All located on 2.36 Acres.
